      "summary": "<p>Google 的開源模型 Gemma 系列自推出以來累計下載超過 4 億次。第四代 Gemma 4 首度改用 Apache 2.0 授權，企業可完全自由商用，不再受 Google 自訂條款限制。</p><p>Gemma 4 支援 140 種以上語言、原生函數呼叫，以及影片和音訊輸入。最小的版本只啟動 20 億參數，能在手機、Raspberry Pi 等邊緣裝置離線運行。Google 此舉是為了與 Meta Llama 和中國開源模型搶開發者生態。</p>",
      "chart": "<div class='chart-wrap'><div class='chart-title' style='color:#1a1a1a'>Gemma 系列模型演進</div><div class='chart-timeline' style='background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px'><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:8px'><span style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px'>Gemma 1</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>2B / 7B 參數</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>Google 自訂授權</span></div><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:8px'><span style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px'>Gemma 2</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>2B–27B 參數</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>Google 自訂授權</span></div><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:8px'><span style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px'>Gemma 3</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>1B–27B 參數</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>Google 自訂授權</span></div><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-top:2px solid #4285f4;padding-top:8px'><span style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px;font-weight:600'>Gemma 4</span><span style='color:#666;font-size:12px'>2B–31B 參數</span><span style='color:#4285f4;font-size:12px;font-weight:600'>Apache 2.0 ✓</span></div></div><div class='chart-source' style='color:#999;font-size:11px;margin-top:6px'>資料來源：Google Blog</div></div>",
