      "summary": "<p>預測市場在美國的法律定位一直曖昧：是金融衍生品，還是線上賭博？三個州（伊利諾、亞利桑那、康乃狄克）選擇後者，對 Kalshi 和 Polymarket 發出禁止令，亞利桑那甚至提起刑事訴訟。</p><p>川普政府的 CFTC 反過來控告這三州，主張預測市場合約屬於「交換契約」，聯邦有專屬管轄權。這是聯邦政府罕見地為加密原生平台出手打官司，背後是預測市場月交易量已突破 80 億美元的現實。</p>",
      "chart": "<div class='chart-wrap'><div class='chart-title' style='color:#1a1a1a'>三州 vs 聯邦：預測市場管轄權之爭</div><div class='chart-row' style='background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px'><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee'><span class='chart-row-label' style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px'>伊利諾州</span><span class='chart-row-value' style='color:#d32f2f;font-size:12px'>禁止令</span></div><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee'><span class='chart-row-label' style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px'>亞利桑那州</span><span class='chart-row-value' style='color:#d32f2f;font-size:12px'>禁止令 + 刑事訴訟</span></div><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee'><span class='chart-row-label' style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px'>康乃狄克州</span><span class='chart-row-value' style='color:#d32f2f;font-size:12px'>禁止令</span></div><div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center'><span class='chart-row-label' style='color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px;font-weight:600'>CFTC（聯邦）</span><span class='chart-row-value' style='color:#1565c0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600'>控告三州 → 主張專屬管轄</span></div></div><div class='chart-source' style='color:#999;font-size:11px;margin-top:6px'>資料來源：CFTC、NPR</div></div>",
      "discussions": "<div class='story-discuss'><ol><li><span class='discuss-tag'>官方聲明</span> CFTC 將持續捍衛對這些市場的專屬監管權，保護市場參與者免受州級過度監管 — <a href='https://www.cftc.gov/PressRoom/PressReleases/9206-26'>CFTC 主席 Michael Selig</a></li><li><span class='discuss-tag'>質疑聲音</span> 把運動賽事投注包裝成「交換契約」，不改變它本質上就是賭博的事實 — <a href='https://www.npr.org/2026/04/02/nx-s1-5771635/trump-cftc-kalshi-polymarket-lawsuits'>NPR</a></li><li><span class='discuss-tag'>產業觀點</span> 這場官司的結果將決定整個預測市場產業能否在美國合法生存 — <a href='https://www.coindesk.com/policy/2026/04/02/cftc-sues-illinois-over-state-s-cease-and-desist-letters-against-prediction-markets'>CoinDesk</a></li></ol></div>"
