      "id": "2026-04-03-Block-裁員-40%-Jack-Dorsey-要用-AI-取代中階主管",
      "title": "Block 裁員 4,000 人後，Jack Dorsey 要讓 6,000 人全向他報告——用 AI 取代中階主管",
      "url": "https://fortune.com/2026/04/02/jack-dorsey-roelof-botha-ai-middle-management/",
