      "url": "https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/apollo-caps-private-credit-fund-withdrawals-as-requests-hit-11",
      "title": "Apollo 限制贖回只付 45 美分，私募信貸的「流動性假象」破裂",
      "sources": [
        {
          "name": "Bloomberg",
          "url": "https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/apollo-caps-private-credit-fund-withdrawals-as-requests-hit-11"
        },
        {
          "name": "CNBC",
          "url": "https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/23/apollo-private-credit-fund-gives-investors-only-45percent-of-requested-withdrawals.html"
        },
        {
          "name": "Milk Road",
          "url": "https://mrcrypto.milkroad.com/p/software-is-a-dead-asset"
        }
      ],
      "summary": "<p>Apollo、Blue Owl、Ares 這幾家機構管理的私募信貸基金，過去幾年是華爾街最熱門的資產類別之一。賣點是「像存款一樣穩定、比公債報酬高」。不過私募信貸有個結構性問題：底層資產是企業貸款，流動性遠不如公債，基金卻向投資人承諾每季可贖回。當贖回潮一來，這個承諾就會打折。Apollo 的 $250 億旗艦基金 ADS 就是最新的案例。</p>\n        <p>今年第一季 ADS 收到 11.2% 的贖回請求，超過 $15 億美元要出場。Apollo 啟動合約中的 5% 季度上限，只兌付了 $7.3 億——等於投資人每要求贖回 1 美元，只拿回 45 美分。全產業情況類似：貝萊德、摩根士丹利、高盛旗下的私募信貸基金，Q1 合計收到超過 $100 億贖回請求，只兌付了約七成。高盛分析師預測，未來兩年零售端私募信貸可能流失 $450 億到 $700 億資產。違約率已升至 5.8%，其中兩到三成的曝險集中在 SaaS 公司——AI 正在侵蝕這些借款企業的護城河。</p>",
      "chart": "<div class=\"chart-wrap\">\n          <div style=\"background:#0a0a0a;color:#e0e0e0;max-width:800px;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;font-family:-apple-system,'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;\">2026 Q1 主要私募信貸基金贖回情況</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin-bottom:20px;\">投資人要求贖回 vs 實際兌付金額（億美元）</div>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;\">\n              <div>\n                <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;\"><span>Apollo ADS</span><span>$15 億 → 兌付 $7.3 億（45%）</span></div>\n                <div style=\"background:#222;border-radius:4px;height:24px;position:relative;\">\n                  <div style=\"background:#c0392b;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:4px;position:absolute;opacity:0.3;\"></div>\n                  <div style=\"background:#c0392b;width:45%;height:100%;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;\"><span>全產業合計</span><span>$101 億 → 兌付 ~$70 億（~70%）</span></div>\n                <div style=\"background:#222;border-radius:4px;height:24px;position:relative;\">\n                  <div style=\"background:#e67e22;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:4px;position:absolute;opacity:0.3;\"></div>\n                  <div style=\"background:#e67e22;width:70%;height:100%;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;\"><span>Blue Owl OBDC II</span><span>永久關閉贖回（200% 贖回暴增）</span></div>\n                <div style=\"background:#222;border-radius:4px;height:24px;position:relative;\">\n                  <div style=\"background:#8e44ad;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:4px;opacity:0.5;\"></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:16px;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #333;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;color:#888;\">\n              <span>違約率 5.8%（近年新高）</span>\n              <span>高盛預估兩年流失 $450-700 億</span>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-align:right;font-size:11px;color:#666;margin-top:12px;\">資料來源：Bloomberg · CNBC / 區塊勢整理</div>",
