      "url": "https://www.theblock.co/post/390837/the-optimistic-case-for-crypto-in-2026-with-bitwise-cio-matt-hougan",
      "title": "Bitwise：4 月 15 日報稅截止後，加密貨幣的賣壓才會真正消失",
      "sources": [
        {
          "name": "The Block",
          "url": "https://www.theblock.co/post/390837/the-optimistic-case-for-crypto-in-2026-with-bitwise-cio-matt-hougan"
        },
        {
          "name": "Milk Road",
          "url": "https://mrcrypto.milkroad.com/p/software-is-a-dead-asset"
        },
        {
          "name": "Blockchain Magazine",
          "url": "https://blockchainmagazine.net/crypto-market-today-2026-03-29/"
        }
      ],
      "summary": "<p>比特幣目前在 $66,000 附近震盪，恐懼與貪婪指數跌到 9——接近歷史最低。市場上有各種解釋：伊朗局勢、私募信貸風暴、全球風險資產拋售。不過 Bitwise 投資長 Matt Hougan 指出一個被忽略的因素：美國報稅日。2025 年初的川普迷因幣暴漲和選後大漲，讓投資人帳面上有可觀的資本利得稅要繳。4 月 15 日是報稅截止日，這些人正在賣幣籌錢繳稅。</p>\n        <p>Hougan 的觀察是：加密貨幣歷史上經常在報稅日前走弱、報稅日後反彈。今年的稅務賣壓特別重，因為 2025 年的獲利特別高。一旦 4/15 過後賣壓消失，搭配 CLARITY Act 可能在年中通過、以及中東局勢若降溫，就是反彈的窗口。Bitwise 分析師仍預期比特幣先到 $80,000 的機率高於跌到 $60,000。22V Research 的 Jordy Visser 則從更宏觀的角度補充：七大科技股的成長敘事正在被 AI 瓦解，退休基金仍需要報酬，比特幣是下一個選項。</p>",
      "chart": "<div class=\"chart-wrap\">\n          <div style=\"background:#0a0a0a;color:#e0e0e0;max-width:800px;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;font-family:-apple-system,'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;\">2026 Q1 加密市場情緒時間軸</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#888;margin-bottom:20px;\">恐懼與貪婪指數 · 關鍵事件標記</div>\n            <div style=\"position:relative;height:80px;margin-bottom:8px;\">\n              <div style=\"position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:50%;height:2px;background:#333;\"></div>\n              <div style=\"position:absolute;left:5%;top:10px;text-align:center;\">\n                <div style=\"width:10px;height:10px;background:#27ae60;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto;\"></div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-top:4px;\">1月<br>指數 65</div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"position:absolute;left:30%;top:10px;text-align:center;\">\n                <div style=\"width:10px;height:10px;background:#e67e22;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto;\"></div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-top:4px;\">2月<br>指數 30</div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"position:absolute;left:55%;top:2px;text-align:center;\">\n                <div style=\"width:14px;height:14px;background:#c0392b;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto;border:2px solid #e74c3c;\"></div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#e74c3c;margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;\">3/30<br>指數 9</div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"position:absolute;left:75%;top:10px;text-align:center;\">\n                <div style=\"width:10px;height:10px;background:#f39c12;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto;border:2px dashed #f39c12;\"></div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#f39c12;margin-top:4px;\">4/15<br>報稅日</div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"position:absolute;left:92%;top:10px;text-align:center;\">\n                <div style=\"width:10px;height:10px;background:#27ae60;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto;border:2px dashed #27ae60;\"></div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#27ae60;margin-top:4px;\">反彈?</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:20px;display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:12px;\">\n              <div style=\"flex:1;padding:10px;background:#1a1a2e;border-radius:6px;\">\n                <div style=\"color:#c0392b;font-weight:600;\">BTC $66K</div>\n                <div style=\"color:#888;\">Fear & Greed: 9</div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"flex:1;padding:10px;background:#1a1a2e;border-radius:6px;\">\n                <div style=\"color:#f39c12;font-weight:600;\">Bitwise 預測</div>\n                <div style=\"color:#888;\">先到 $80K > $60K</div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"flex:1;padding:10px;background:#1a1a2e;border-radius:6px;\">\n                <div style=\"color:#27ae60;font-weight:600;\">催化劑</div>\n                <div style=\"color:#888;\">報稅日 + CLARITY</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-align:right;font-size:11px;color:#666;margin-top:12px;\">資料來源：Bitwise · Milk Road · Blockchain Magazine / 區塊勢整理</div>",
